			<div class="content" id="post-content-4409433">
									

<p>A few of the avatar pictures are showing broken on my end, but that may be because I'm using the school network and it has&#8230; odd&#8230; blocking policies that only the administration can override (and I'm not going to go defend why I'm getting paid to read SCPs). I'll check again on my home network later.</p>
<p>Any rate, I thoroughly enjoyed this one. The format of twitter style posts can be a bit jarring, but there was enough going on here to make it work. Doesn't hurt that Deer School is one of my favorite (underutilized) GOIs. +1</p>

							</div>

								
					
